    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos domnus
                            <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/303" key="#Marquis/duke">Arigis</persName> summus <rs
                            key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs> genti Langobardorum, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3657" key="#Other_palatine_officer"
                            >Griserissi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">stolesari</rs> nostro, tibi <persName
                            ref="#people/3658" key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">Muncolani</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldio</rs> nostro pueri duos, id est
                            <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                ><name ref="Egyptus">Egipto</name> et <name ref="Mauritanus"
                                >Mauretano</name></rs>, solas eorum personas, qui fuerint de
                            <placeName ref="#places/3469"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property #Slave"><rs key="#Actio"
                                >atto</rs> Cassianense</placeName>, quem modo <persName
                            ref="#people/3659" key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">Cunari</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldio</rs> nostro tenere videtur,
                        quatinus amodo et deinceps habeas et in tuo deteneas servitium ipsi nominati
                        pueris tam tu qui super Muncola quam etiam et filiis filiorum tuorum, et
                        nullus ex nostris gastaldeis aut actionariis vel quispia homo contra ea que
                        nostra concessit potestas quandoque ire presumat, sed nostram concessione
                        omni in tempore roborata atque inviolata perhennis temporibus permaneat.
                        Quod vero preceptus concessionis ex iussione nominate potestatis per
                            <persName ref="#people/3490" key="#Other_palatine_officer"
                            >Gaydemari</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">referendario</rs> scripsi ego <persName
                            ref="#people/3660" key="#Notary">Eudoal</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarias</rs>. Actus <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Beneventus</placeName> in palatio mensi augusto per
                        indictione secunda. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
